items.name: END
desc: Cross the other axes at their maximum scale value.

items.name: START
desc: Cross the other axes at their minimum scale value.

items.name: VALUE
desc: Cross the other axes at the value specified in the property CrossoverValue.

items.name: ZERO
desc: Cross the other axes at zero.
If zero is not contained in the current scale the value is used which is nearest to zero.
